主意，你很难说服他。在审查项目或代码的时候，有时候他给出的建议非常好，有时候就会比较主观，如果不按照他说的做吧，就得花时间说服他，那就会比较烦<br><br>要怎么和他沟通啊？身边同事就是这样的，真心求教","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":7734,"user_name":"self-discipline","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1024457,"ip_address":"","ucode":"A5AEDCA9ACC68A","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/a1/c9/501a1d02.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1525684090,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"1525684090","product_id":100002401,"comment_content":"我想咨询下,我承认我也是从新手过来的,现在我负责某个小组,七八个人吧,很多时候做代码审核,同样的问题同样的人,一个问题若干次,真让人想那把砍刀砍死他,我又没有开除人的权限,求教,我要如何和这些人相处呢？","like_count":0,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":2166073,"avatar":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/k3YD3y3BzGDSdrwRJyJY4BXsNJibfM4uzOdDVKIAlFApR2FZCLg2ibrZtJ4vuahA3LHLW9GKzH5CMGqCDhWjhZqg/132","nickname":"戒酒的李白","note":"","ucode":"744E1A22761647","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":true},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":544826,"discussion_content":"可以让人统计下每个人的代码问题数，让下属自己意识到问题所在","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1641725883,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":3583,"user_name":"alex","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1013615,"ip_address":"","ucode":"3194B224CD7AC2","user_header":"http://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/Q0j4TwGTfTI98sVPqp4B5YJU8Piao6ic4KeiaDGU0jMUrAqlNaUR4APfWMxkkNUA59O7z11sVQRg95gt3Mb6KTXIA/132","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1519949179,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1519949179","product_id":100002401,"comment_content":"组内的比较好处理，毕竟上下工作交集很多的。跨组就需要点技巧了。有时候真的是私底下也要做好一些关系的。真心有点小累。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":1977,"user_name":"王建Tyrion","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1009595,